📈 Dashboard Features
KPIs Cards – Overview of total employees, attrition rate, average salary, and age.

Department-wise Analysis – Attrition, headcount, and salary comparisons by department.

Demographic Insights – Gender distribution, education level, and experience trends.

Attrition Breakdown – By age, job role, salary, and tenure.

Interactive Filters – Filter by department, gender, age, or education field.

🚀 Results Summary
Identified key causes of employee attrition and performance trends.

Helped HR managers plan targeted retention strategies.

Improved understanding of salary structure and diversity across the company.

Delivered a data-driven HR dashboard for quick and informed decisions.

🔮 Future Enhancements
Predictive analysis for employee attrition risk using ML models.

Integration with real-time HR systems (e.g., Workday, SAP HR).

Add employee satisfaction survey analytics.

Include recruitment pipeline and hiring trend visualization.

